reviews.review_text:
Sounds great! This is a close up, rich sounding FOB.  Nice full bass, without boom or distortion.  The instruments are well-balanced.

This recording by Rango is what an AUD enthusiast's dream!

I Agree.  Beautiful recording. I concur Doctor Unclear.  Exceptionally good recording.  And there are a number of good recordings for this show.  Those D5s were wonderful things!  But the show is only average, though I've always thought average for the Boyz was pretty good.  One of only eight Dews they did in '82.  Jerry sounds good tonight (well relatively good anyway) in the last year he actually did sound half-way decent.  I'm willing to give four stars for Jer's better than average vocals and stellar sound.   I'm only keeping Estimated > onwards and editing out OMSN to fade in U.S. Blues for a great ending.   Thanks Rango.  Nice Job!
